sentences: Kevin Drumm (born 1970) is an experimental musician based in Chicago, United States.
He has also worked with the artist group Simparch, composing a piece for their installation Spec, shown at Documenta XI in Kassel, Germany and at the Renaissance Society in Chicago.
Drumm has received a Foundation for Contemporary Arts Grants to Artists award (2011).
